              "settings": {
                "html": "<section class=\"relative h-[520px] flex items-end overflow-hidden\">\n    <div class=\"absolute inset-0 z-0\">\n      <img class=\"w-full h-full object-cover\" alt=\"\" src=\"https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1502301103665-0b95cc738daf?q=80&w=2000&auto=format&fit=crop\"/>\n      <div class=\"absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-primary/95 via-primary/40 to-primary/10\"></div>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"relative z-10 max-w-container-max mx-auto px-gutter w-full pb-stack-lg\">\n      <span class=\"inline-block bg-secondary-container text-on-secondary-container px-3 py-1 rounded-md text-body-sm font-label-bold uppercase tracking-wider mb-stack-md\">Guide \u00b7 8 min read</span>\n      <h1 class=\"font-h1 text-h1 text-white max-w-4xl mb-stack-md drop-shadow-md\">10 Tips for Your Montenegro Road Trip</h1>\n      <p class=\"text-white/85 font-body-lg max-w-2xl\">From hidden gas stations to the most beautiful viewpoints along the coast \u2014 everything we wish someone had told us before our first drive through Montenegro.</p>\n      <div class=\"flex items-center gap-6 mt-stack-md text-white/80 text-body-sm\">\n        <span class=\"flex items-center gap-2\"><span class=\"material-symbols-outlined text-[18px]\">edit</span> By MontenegroDrive Editorial</span>\n        <span class=\"flex items-center gap-2\"><span class=\"material-symbols-outlined text-[18px]\">schedule</span> 8 min read</span>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </section>",
