                "html": "<section class=\"py-section-padding px-gutter bg-surface-container-low\">\n    <div class=\"max-w-container-max mx-auto\">\n      <h2 class=\"font-h2 text-h2 text-primary mb-stack-lg\">Continue reading</h2>\n      <div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-6\">\n        \n        <a href=\"article-panoramic-routes.html\" class=\"group bg-white rounded-xl overflow-hidden shadow-sm border border-outline-variant/30 hover:shadow-md transition-all block\">\n          <div class=\"aspect-video overflow-hidden\"><img class=\"w-full h-full object-cover group-hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-500\" alt=\"\" src=\"https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1566127992631-137a642a90f4?q=80&w=1200&auto=format&fit=crop\"/></div>\n          <div class=\"p-5\">\n            <h4 class=\"font-h3 text-[18px] text-primary mb-2\">Best Panoramic Routes in Europe</h4>\n            <p class=\"text-body-sm text-secondary\">Eight scenic drives that genuinely earn the clich\u00e9.</p>\n          </div>\n        </a>\n        <a href=\"article-driving-rules.html\" class=\"group bg-white rounded-xl overflow-hidden shadow-sm border border-outline-variant/30 hover:shadow-md transition-all block\">\n          <div class=\"aspect-video overflow-hidden\"><img class=\"w-full h-full object-cover group-hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-500\" alt=\"\" src=\"https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1449965408869-eaa3f722e40d?q=80&w=1200&auto=format&fit=crop\"/></div>\n          <div class=\"p-5\">\n            <h4 class=\"font-h3 text-[18px] text-primary mb-2\">Driving in Montenegro: What You Need to Know</h4>\n            <p class=\"text-body-sm text-secondary\">Speed limits, alcohol policy, road conditions.</p>\n          </div>\n        </a>\n        <a href=\"article-prokletije.html\" class=\"group bg-white rounded-xl overflow-hidden shadow-sm border border-outline-variant/30 hover:shadow-md transition-all block\">\n          <div class=\"aspect-video overflow-hidden\"><img class=\"w-full h-full object-cover group-hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-500\" alt=\"\" src=\"https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1464822759023-fed622ff2c3b?q=80&w=1200&auto=format&fit=crop\"/></div>\n          <div class=\"p-5\">\n            <h4 class=\"font-h3 text-[18px] text-primary mb-2\">Prokletije: The Cursed Mountains</h4>\n            <p class=\"text-body-sm text-secondary\">A 4x4 guide to the Balkans' most dramatic range.</p>\n          </div>\n        </a>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </section>",
